==College career==
{{multiple image
| align     = left
| direction = horizontal
| header    = [[2013<U+2013>14 Michigan Wolverines men's basketball team|Michigan]]&ndash;[[2013<U+2013>14 Minnesota Golden Gophers men's basketball team|Minnesota]] [[2013<U+2013>14 Big Ten Conference men's basketball season|2013<U+2013>14 Big Ten season]] opener
| width     = 160

